  "detailed_description": "In Promenade you have to collect golden cogs to fix the great elevator and unlock new worlds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To do so, you can engage with a bunch of diverse activities, like puzzles, races, cute NPCs, and many secrets scattered everywhere by using a dynamic moveset.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Whether you like puzzles that require lateral thinking, technical platforming, or just wandering around, there's always something interesting awaiting for you around the corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use object's properties to your advantage : double jump by throwing an object down, glide when holding a chicken, run at insane speed with the rocket and a lot more to experiment !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f68d19f86e7d317b793c83d11c57abb3.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=175 /></span><br><br>And since you only need to collect some of the cogs to progress, you can follow your instinct and only engage with what interests you the most.<br>Will it be platforming challenges ? Interacting with colorful characters ? Or facing the bosses that dwell in dungeons ?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/b701092c5a1785a2b7b5ed9a50714c87.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/b701092c5a1785a2b7b5ed9a50714c87.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/b701092c5a1785a2b7b5ed9a50714c87.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Wether you're a completionist, a cozy gamer, a speedrunner or a collectathon lover, you'll find your way to finish the game the way you like !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/3dc91e64c8d76a09a3c64fb40111d746.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=175 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In Promenade you have to collect golden cogs to fix the great elevator and unlock new worlds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/021af4b2c1a3b1fa11280e81c0e87a2e.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To do so, you can engage with a bunch of diverse activities, like puzzles, races, cute NPCs, and many secrets scattered everywhere by using a dynamic moveset.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/1404ef2f3135df32ce6b87a60bc9e4d8.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Whether you like puzzles that require lateral thinking, technical platforming, or just wandering around, there's always something interesting awaiting for you around the corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f0860cd8876da4e30662bbd5316b5391.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use object's properties to your advantage : double jump by throwing an object down, glide when holding a chicken, run at insane speed with the rocket and a lot more to experiment !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/f68d19f86e7d317b793c83d11c57abb3.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=175 /></span><br><br>And since you only need to collect some of the cogs to progress, you can follow your instinct and only engage with what interests you the most.<br>Will it be platforming challenges ? Interacting with colorful characters ? Or facing the bosses that dwell in dungeons ?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/b701092c5a1785a2b7b5ed9a50714c87.poster.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/b701092c5a1785a2b7b5ed9a50714c87.webm?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/b701092c5a1785a2b7b5ed9a50714c87.mp4?t=1737564431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Wether you're a completionist, a cozy gamer, a speedrunner or a collectathon lover, you'll find your way to finish the game the way you like !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781260/extras/3dc91e64c8d76a09a3c64fb40111d746.avif?t=1737564431\" width=600 height=175 /></span>",
